<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 14:21:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>科技股抛售引发避险情绪，比特币触及两周低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-tech-selloff-sparks-risk-off-mood</link><description>由于科技股的抛售打击了风险资产，比特币跌至近两周低点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iD6CSZF2Ssmo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 09:33:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-tech-selloff-sparks-risk-off-mood</guid></item><item><title>加密货币评论家 Nouriel Roubini 发现了区块链的用途</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/crypto-critic-nouriel-roubini-finds-a-use-for-the-blockchain</link><description>经济学家努里尔·鲁比尼 (Nouriel Roubini) 因预测 2008 年金融危机以及后来对加密货币的尖锐批评而闻名，他正在将他的一款投资产品放在区块链上。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ilit_FMYS38Q/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/crypto-critic-nouriel-roubini-finds-a-use-for-the-blockchain</guid></item><item><title>加纳创立的加密货币交易所在股权融资中着眼于外国人</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/ghanaian-founded-crypto-exchange-eyes-foreigners-in-equity-round</link><description>Hyro Exchange 是加纳第一家成立的加密货币交易所，在完成最近的种子融资后，正在考虑增发股票，以加速在加纳和主要非洲市场的扩张。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0Xn2y67F9Wc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 10:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/ghanaian-founded-crypto-exchange-eyes-foreigners-in-equity-round</guid></item><item><title>Michael Saylor 的策略是使用普通股购买 3490 万美元的比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-22/michael-saylor-s-strategy-buys-34-9-million-of-bitcoin-using-common-stock</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 购买了 3940 万美元的比特币，尽管早些时候承诺转向永久优先股，但连续第三周再次依靠其普通股为购买加密货币提供资金。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/inhz.E4_pC_s/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 12:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-22/michael-saylor-s-strategy-buys-34-9-million-of-bitcoin-using-common-stock</guid></item></channel></rss>